comments: Siakam (TOR) swipes down with his left hand to contest Adebayo's (MIA) upward shooting motion and makes legal contact with the ball.
Adebayo (MIA) brushes Barnes' (TOR) left leg and arm as he contests his shot near the rim, and marginal contact occurs.
Barnes (TOR) makes illegal contact with Adebayo's (MIA) left arm during his driving shot attempt.
Tucker (MIA) gathers the loose ball while in the air and lands with his left foot to complete the pass.
Tucker (MIA) legally dislodges the ball from Siakam's (TOR) hands to force the steal.
Siakam (TOR) and Tucker (MIA) engage and disengage with one another in an attempt to secure the loose ball.
VanVleet (TOR) cleanly deflects the ball in Butler's (MIA) hands during his jump shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) briefly grasps Adebayo's (MIA) left arm during the rebound, and marginal contact occurs.
Barnes (TOR) blocks the driving shot attempt by Herro (MIA) after it touches the backboard.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding Siakam (TOR).
Siakam (TOR) brushes Herro's (MIA) right arm, and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) steps into Strus' (MIA) space and initiates foot to foot contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
